                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant G</hi> 20.) I was sent for, and found this property concealed under the prisoner's bed—the prosecutrix owned it—the prisoner had denied having any property at all.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
