                  </hi>. I found a sovereign, eight half-crowns, and seven shil<lb></lb>lings, in the prisoner's room—she said it was given to her by a gentleman last March—in going to the station, she said, "You will not find the bed<lb></lb>gown; I have not got it"—I said, "You said so about the other things"—she said, "The door was open and 1 went in and took them."</p>
               <p>
